          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The areas of the photopeaks of the corresponding",
                " gamma-lines of the radioisotopes under",
                " consideration obtained as a result of gamma-",
                " spectroscopic measurements were used to extract",
                " their yield Y, which in this work is defined as",
                " the number of radioisotope nuclei formed in the",
                " target per second of its irradiation with",
                " bremsstrahlung photons. The Y were obtained",
                " using the formula (1) of the article.",
                "The final estimate for Y was taken as the average",
                " value over multiple measurements, Y-exp which",
                " is presented as formula (2) of the article.",
                "The weighted and averaged over the",
                " bremsstrahlung photon spectrum cross sections",
                " obtained using formula (3) of the article are",
                " presented."
              ]
            }
          ],
