          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "For the first time, at intermediate photon",
                " energies (below the GeV energy region), inclusive",
                " photodisintegration reactions of manganese",
                " 55Mn(g,X)46Sc, 55Mn(g,X)47Sc and 55Mn(g,X)48Sc",
                " were studied.",
                "The experimental results are an integral value",
                " expressed as a convolution of two functions:",
                " the cross-section and the photon distribution",
                " function. The experimental data are presented as a",
                " flux-weighted average cross sections."
              ]
            }
          ],
